WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:01.927
Buone notizie:

00:00:01.927 --> 00:00:04.708
per questo non serve il terminal!

00:00:04.708 --> 00:00:07.488
Apriremo un VS Code completo direttamente

00:00:07.488 --> 00:00:08.415
nel browser,

00:00:08.415 --> 00:00:09.806
creeremo alcuni file,

00:00:09.806 --> 00:00:12.587
eseguiremo qualche comando e vedremo il

00:00:12.587 --> 00:00:15.367
kernel tenere tutto dentro il repo.

00:00:16.126 --> 00:00:16.993
Ecco l'idea.

00:00:16.993 --> 00:00:19.593
L'editor non gira sul tuo laptop.

00:00:19.593 --> 00:00:22.194
Gira dentro il sandbox del repo

00:00:22.194 --> 00:00:23.061
sul server,

00:00:23.061 --> 00:00:25.661
e il tuo browser ci accede

00:00:25.661 --> 00:00:27.395
tramite un tunnel SSH.

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:29.129
Quindi l'albero dei file,

00:00:29.129 --> 00:00:31.729
il terminal integrato e qualsiasi cosa

00:00:31.729 --> 00:00:34.330
tu avvii da lì vedono esattamente

00:00:34.330 --> 00:00:36.497
quello che vede il repo,

00:00:36.497 --> 00:00:37.364
e nient'altro.

00:00:40.649 --> 00:00:41.364
One command.

00:00:41.364 --> 00:00:43.867
The CLI installs the editor server on

00:00:43.867 --> 00:00:44.939
the machine once,

00:00:44.939 --> 00:00:47.084
starts it inside the repo sandbox,

00:00:47.084 --> 00:00:48.157
opens a tunnel,

00:00:48.157 --> 00:00:49.944
and hands you a link.

00:00:49.944 --> 00:00:51.374
No local VS Code,

00:00:51.374 --> 00:00:53.162
no extensions to set up.

00:00:56.162 --> 00:00:58.690
Quell'URL è il tuo editor.

00:00:58.690 --> 00:01:00.713
Funziona da qualsiasi OS,

00:01:00.713 --> 00:01:03.241
l'unico requisito è un browser.

00:01:03.764 --> 00:01:04.545
Ed eccolo:

00:01:04.545 --> 00:01:05.326
VS Code,

00:01:05.326 --> 00:01:07.279
in una scheda del browser.

00:01:07.279 --> 00:01:10.013
L'albero dei file a sinistra mostra il

00:01:10.013 --> 00:01:10.404
repo,

00:01:10.404 --> 00:01:11.966
e solo il repo.

00:01:16.264 --> 00:01:17.762
Creiamo un file vero,

00:01:17.762 --> 00:01:19.259
senza usare il terminal.

00:01:19.259 --> 00:01:20.383
Un nuovo editor,

00:01:20.383 --> 00:01:21.880
un paio di righe,

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.501
e salviamo come notes slash todo punto

00:01:24.501 --> 00:01:24.876
md.

00:01:24.876 --> 00:01:27.497
La cartella appare a sinistra non appena

00:01:27.497 --> 00:01:28.620
arriva nel repo.

00:01:34.764 --> 00:01:37.058
Anche il terminal integrato funziona,

00:01:37.058 --> 00:01:39.351
ed ecco il nostro file.

00:01:39.351 --> 00:01:42.103
Ora proviamo a guardare fuori dal

00:01:42.103 --> 00:01:42.562
repo:

00:01:42.562 --> 00:01:43.480
permission denied.

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:44.856
Non è un'impostazione,

00:01:44.856 --> 00:01:46.232
è il kernel.

00:01:53.764 --> 00:01:56.019
Same repo from the plain terminal:

00:01:56.019 --> 00:01:58.274
the working directory is the repo,

00:01:58.274 --> 00:02:00.530
the files are the repo's files.

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:06.052
Il terminal e l'editor concordano:

00:02:06.052 --> 00:02:08.269
è lo stesso sandbox.

00:02:11.572 --> 00:02:14.139
And the file we created in

00:02:14.139 --> 00:02:15.423
the browser editor?

00:02:15.423 --> 00:02:16.279
Right here.

00:02:16.279 --> 00:02:18.846
Files made in VS Code are

00:02:18.846 --> 00:02:20.130
real repo files,

00:02:20.130 --> 00:02:20.558
instantly.

00:02:22.308 --> 00:02:23.712
Creato nel browser,

00:02:23.712 --> 00:02:25.115
leggibile dal terminal.

00:02:25.115 --> 00:02:26.519
Un solo repo,

00:02:26.519 --> 00:02:27.454
due porte.

00:02:30.776 --> 00:02:32.307
Now try to leave.

00:02:32.307 --> 00:02:34.604
Listing the root of the server:

00:02:34.604 --> 00:02:35.370
permission denied.

00:02:35.370 --> 00:02:37.284
The kernel scopes the editor,

00:02:37.284 --> 00:02:38.049
its terminal,

00:02:38.049 --> 00:02:40.729
and every child process to this repo.

00:02:42.479 --> 00:02:44.020
Negato dal kernel,

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:45.561
non dalla configurazione.

00:02:48.857 --> 00:02:50.312
Other users' homes?

00:02:50.312 --> 00:02:51.283
Also denied.

00:02:51.283 --> 00:02:54.193
Whatever runs inside this sandbox —

00:02:54.193 --> 00:02:54.679
editors,

00:02:54.679 --> 00:02:55.164
terminals,

00:02:55.164 --> 00:02:58.074
build tools — ends at the

00:02:58.074 --> 00:02:59.045
repo's walls.

00:03:00.795 --> 00:03:02.768
Il sandbox non ha eccezioni.

00:03:02.768 --> 00:03:04.347
Questo è il punto.

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:05.782
Browser,

00:03:05.782 --> 00:03:06.406
editor,

00:03:06.406 --> 00:03:07.029
terminal:

00:03:07.029 --> 00:03:08.276
stesso sandbox,

00:03:08.276 --> 00:03:09.523
stesse regole.

00:03:09.523 --> 00:03:12.640
Prossimamente arriva la funzionalità su

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:15.756
cui si basa tutto questo,

00:03:15.756 --> 00:03:17.003
il forking.

00:03:17.003 --> 00:03:18.873
Questa ti piacerà.
